metadata.name: Anatani Kimeta #1/10
metadata.description:
Anatani Kimeta by Noriko Shakti

Music Video


This song is a reflection of Noriko’s adventure and practice – music production & composing in Tokyo, Indian classical music training & research in Kolkata, and songwriting & singing influenced by Japanese music.


100% of the NFT profit will go to MUZIX foundation for supporting exceptional musicians with music education.
